data.description: Gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 Bathroom bi-level home situated on 1.68 acres in Manalapan! This home features stainless steel kitchen appliances, hardwood flooring, a built-in humidifier, and much more! Entertain your guest in your gorgeous yard with a large heated in-ground pool! The storage shed has electricity and the driveway has plenty of space for parking. Don't miss out on this well-kept home!
